                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8814" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1348</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1743 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西水股份股权投资会计核算方法多次变更之谜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The mystery of the multiple changes in the accounting method of equity investment in Xishui shares</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钟希余，魏李强，黄子晔</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湘潭大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古西水创业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西水股份；长期股权投资；金融资产；会计核算方法变更；监管关注；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Xishui shares; long-term equity investment; financial assets; change in accounting method; regulatory concerns</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上市公司出于不同动机，可能会对所持股权投资的会计核算方法进行变更，进而影响报表净利润。本案例描述了西水股份并购天安财险后由于政策环境变化面临困境，通过将所持兴业银行股权由“可供出售金融资产”变更为“长期股权投资”的权益法核算后，产生20.86亿元净利润，短暂维持住投资者信心。之后天安财险由于经营情况持续恶化，投资资产突然曝出巨额减值，西水股份再次使用变更股权投资会计核算方法的手段，对所持天安财险股权由“长期股权投资”变更为“其他权益工具投资”进行核算，使归属于上市公司股东净利润增加（亏损减少）183.68 亿元。这两次变更行为都对财务报表产生了重大影响。本案例旨在帮助学生理解股权投资的不同类型以及股权投资会计核算的不同方法，进而引导学生思考上市公司变更股权投资会计核算方法的真实动机，锻炼学生站在监管方和投资者等不同角度思考如何应对的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> Listed companies may change the accounting method of their equity investments for different motives, which may affect the net profit. This case describes that after the acquisition of Tian&#39;an Property and Casualty Insurance by Xishui Stock, the company faced difficulties due to the change of the policy environment, and then changed the accounting method of its equity interest in Industrial Bank from &quot;available-for-sale financial assets&quot; to &quot;long-term equity investment&quot;, resulting in a net profit of RMB 2.086 billion. After that, due to the continuous deterioration of Tian&#39;an property and casualty insurance, Xishui shares once again used the means of changing the accounting method,The change in accounting method for the equity interest in Tianan Financial Insurance from &quot;long-term equity investment&quot; to &quot;investment in other equity instruments&quot; resulted in an increase in net profit attributable to shareholders of the listed company of RMB18,368 million (decrease in loss). Both changes had a significant impact on the financial statements.This case aims to help students understand the different types of equity investment and the different methods of accounting for equity investment, and exercise the ability of students to think about how to deal with the situation from different perspectives such as the regulator and investors.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《中级财务会计》、《财务管理》、《财务会计理论与实务》、《财务管理理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业股权投资的类型；股权投资会计核算方法变更的不同类型；股权投资会计核算方法变更的动机</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
